---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import FooterBanner from "../ui/FooterBanner.astro";
---

<footer class="bg-white py-10 px-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col gap-10">

        <FooterBanner />

        <div class="bg-orange-500 text-white/90 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 sm:p-10 flex flex-col gap-8 shadow-lg border border-white/20">

            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-10 border-b border-white/20 pb-8">

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8 sm:gap-12">
                    <a href="https://rnt-consulta.sectur.gob.mx/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col items-center group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <img
                                src="https://storage.googleapis.com/tudestinomx_bucket/assets/img/sectur_logo.png"
                                alt="Secretaría de Turismo"
                                class="h-10 sm:h-12 md:h-14 w-auto object-contain mb-3 drop-shadow-md"
                        />
                        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded shadow-md w-44 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] border border-white/30">
                            <div class="bg-[#b90309] text-white text-center py-1 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                                SECTUR No.
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-black text-white text-center py-1 font-mono">
                                0423005c2dd75
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </a>

                    <div class="flex items-center hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <img
                                src="https://storage.googleapis.com/tudestinomx_bucket/assets/img/sat_logo.png"
                                alt="Hacienda y Crédito Público"
                                class="h-10 sm:h-12 md:h-14 w-auto object-contain drop-shadow-md"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex gap-5">
                    <a href="https://fb.com/tudestinomexicoo" target="_blank">
                        <Icon size={30} class="text-white hover:scale-110 hover:text-orange-200 transition-all cursor-pointer" name="bxl:facebook" />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://instagram.com/tudestinomexico" target="_blank">
                        <Icon size={30} class="text-white hover:scale-110 hover:text-orange-200 transition-all cursor-pointer" name="bxl:instagram" />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://tiktok.com/@tudestinomexico" target="_blank">
                        <Icon size={30} class="text-white hover:scale-110 hover:text-orange-200 transition-all cursor-pointer" name="bxl:tiktok" />
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://youtube.com/@tudestinomexico" target="_blank">
                        <Icon size={30} class="text-white hover:scale-110 hover:text-orange-200 transition-all cursor-pointer" name="bxl:youtube" />
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center md:items-end gap-8 text-xs sm:text-sm">

                <div class="text-center md:text-left leading-relaxed space-y-1.5">
                    <p class="font-bold text-white text-sm sm:text-base">© TU DESTINO MX ROLANDO X MEXICO S.A. de C.V.</p>
                    <p>Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
                    <p>No nos hacemos responsables por fotografías no actualizadas por la cadena o proveedor distinguido.</p>
                    <p class="mt-2 flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-1.5">
                        <span class="font-bold text-white">Teléfono:</span>
                        <a href="tel:+529989806611" class="hover:text-white hover:underline transition-colors">(998) 980 6611</a>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10">
                    <a
                            href="/terminos-condiciones"
                            class="font-semibold text-white/80 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-white transition-all italic text-center whitespace-nowrap"
                    >
                        Nuestros términos y condiciones.
                    </a>
                    <a
                            href="/privacidad"
                            class="font-semibold text-white/80 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-white transition-all italic text-center whitespace-nowrap"
                    >
                        Aviso de privacidad
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</footer>

<style>
</style>